Variable.Name: DayOfWeek
Variable.Comment: Current day of the week (between 1 and 7)

Variable.Name: Idx_In_TZM
Variable.Comment: Index used to switch time zone.

Variable.Name: Rule_RegArr_In_TZM
Variable.Comment: Time zone rule (TZREG_ARRAY_TZM) in POSIX format.

Variable.Name: Rule_RegArr_TZM
Variable.Comment: Time zone rule (TZREG_ARRAY_TZM) in POSIX format.

Variable.Name: Rule_Str_In_TZM
Variable.Comment: Time zone rule (STRING) in POSIX format.

Variable.Name: Rule_Str_TZM
Variable.Comment: Time zone rule (STRING) in POSIX format.

Variable.Name: IN
Variable.Comment: if Rising edge, starts increasing internal timer. If Falling Edge, stops and resets internal timer

Variable.Name: Q
Variable.Comment: if TRUE, programmed time is elapsed

Variable.Name: Write_TZM
Variable.Comment: Writes the correspondent rule of Idx_In_TZM. (works on the edge)
